 <ThingDef ParentName="HatMakeableBase">
    <defName>KP_Field_Hat_Arctic</defName>
    <label>Field Hat (Polar)</label>
    <description>Though a similar design to other cold weather gear, this one is more than it appears. This headwear features the same mesh heating network as the Polar Uniform, though with a few modifications, mainly it can be powered by both dead skin cells and shed hair to ensure comfortable warmth during the coldest of environments. Much like its companion piece, this one requires additional research for it to be produced.</description>
	<techLevel>Industrial</techLevel>	
    
    <recipeMaker>
      <researchPrerequisite>ArcticUniforms</researchPrerequisite>
	  </recipeMaker>

    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Headgear/FieldHatArctic/FieldHatArctic</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
	    <shaderType>CutoutComplex</shaderType>
